#

Tuna Avocado Wrap

10 min
$3.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

FishSoy (if using soy sauce)

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow CarbGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Lunch

Tags:

Quick MealHealthyLunch

Description

A quick and healthy wrap filled with protein-rich tuna and creamy avocado, perfect for a light lunch.

Ingredients

  • whole wheat tortilla: 1
  • canned tuna (in water): 1 can
  • avocado: 1/2
  • lettuce leaves: 2-3
  • cherry tomatoes: 5-6
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
